ption><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 08:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-its-vessels-passing-through-tokara-strait-have-right-transit-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>郑在美国公开赛最新一场女子比赛中击败维克奇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-defeats-vekic-us-opens-latest-finish-womens-match-2024-09-02/</link><description>郑沁文在巴黎奥运会冠军争夺战的复赛中以7-6(2) 4-6 6-2击败克罗地亚选手唐娜·维基奇，晋级美国公开赛四分之一决赛。锦标赛的历史。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 06:50:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-defeats-vekic-us-opens-latest-finish-womens-match-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济不景气加速肥胖率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-malaise-seen-accelerating-obesity-rates-2024-09-02/</link><description>随着中国建造的房屋和桥梁减少，消费者购买更便宜、不太健康的食物，随着工厂和农场投资自动化，新的财政挑战正在出现：中国的肥胖率可能会增长得更快，并增加医疗费用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 05:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-malaise-seen-accelerating-obesity-rates-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：绘制工资单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-02/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 04:37:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国对阿里巴巴进行监管审查期间的关键事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/key-events-during-chinas-regulatory-scrutiny-alibaba-2024-09-02/</link><description>中国国家市场监督管理总局 (SAMR) 周五表示，继 2021 年因垄断行为被处以创纪录的 27.5 亿美元罚款后，阿里巴巴集团已完成三年“整改”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 04:25:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/key-events-during-chinas-regulatory-scrutiny-alibaba-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国经济的改善，亚洲工厂出现初步复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asian-factories-show-tentative-signs-recovery-china-improves-2024-09-02/</link><description>周一的私人调查显示，包括中国制造业在内的亚洲工厂在八月份显示出初步复苏的迹象，芯片制造商受益于强劲的需求，但经济逆风迫在眉睫。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 03:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asian-factories-show-tentative-signs-recovery-china-improves-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>预计亏损 26 亿美元后，香港新世界发展股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shares-hong-kongs-new-world-development-plunge-after-26-bln-loss-forecast-2024-09-02/</link><description>香港主要房地产开发商新世界发展公司 (New World Development) 预计截至 6 月份的财政年度净亏损高达 200 亿港元（合 26 亿美元），其股价暴跌 14%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 02:46:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shares-hong-kongs-new-world-development-plunge-after-26-bln-loss-forecast-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>总统表示，如果中国想要台湾，也应该从俄罗斯手中夺回土地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/if-china-wants-taiwan-it-should-also-take-back-land-russia-president-says-2024-09-02/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德在接受台湾媒体采访时表示，如果中国对台湾的主张涉及领土完整，那么它也应该从俄罗斯收回19世纪中国最后一个王朝签署的土地。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 02:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/if-china-wants-taiwan-it-should-also-take-back-land-russia-president-says-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-09-02/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 01:54:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促欧盟在南海问题上“客观公正”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-eu-be-objective-fair-south-china-sea-issue-2024-09-02/</link><description>在欧盟对周末发生的事件发表评论后，中国敦促欧盟在南海问题上“客观、公正”，谨慎言行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 01:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-eu-be-objective-fair-south-china-sea-issue-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国数据疲弱和预期 OPEC+ 供应增加，油价扩大跌幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-losses-prospect-higher-opec-supply-2024-09-02/</link><description>由于预期 OPEC+ 从 10 月起产量将增加，而中国和美国需求疲软的迹象引发了对未来消费增长的担忧，周一油价扩大跌幅。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:31:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-extends-losses-prospect-higher-opec-supply-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市和美国期货九月开局不利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-09-02/</link><description>周一股市小幅下跌，投资者准备迎接充满数据的一周，最终将公布美国就业报告，该报告可能决定本月预期的降息是常规降息还是大幅降息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:29:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-09-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>